  visitDate: "2021-06-02T15:19:44.911Z",
  nextVisitDate: "2021-06-02T15:19:44.911Z",
  patientCode: patientDTO.code,
  age: 18,
  sex: "M",
  note: "out patient consultation",
  prog_year: 18,
  disease: diseaseDTO,
  disease2: diseaseDTO,
  disease3: diseaseDTO,
  newPatient: "N",

  referralTo: "R",

export default opdDTO;
